{"tid":1591035,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"蔣志光入行34年惡補英文仍追電影夢","createTime":"2019-09-24T03:48:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T17:27:14.000Z","uid":44730,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"eaa2cc0569d0c43e2d73adc3985fd76c1d7d3d41","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:48:19.000Z","msg":"58歲蔣志光生於長洲，小學畢業後輟學，跟爸爸學做上海裁縫。10多歲時，爸爸就去世，他便轉做打蠟和工廠工人養家。後來發覺真正興趣在電影，便一邊做片場小工，一邊讀夜校，又睇外國電影增加英文能力。中五畢業後擔任獨立製作的電影幕後，由低做起，最高曾擔任副導演，期間不斷讀英文電影書籍。學英文時開始培養填詞的興趣，加上有感本地獨立電影公司難生存，失業大半年後終轉行音樂幕前與幕後事業，希望較易獲得賞識。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://resource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk/res/v3/image/content/2455000/2457880/15_600.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresource01-proxy.ulifestyle.com.hk%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2455000%2F2457880%2F15_600.jpg&h=0e402447&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5c9e88b64aac345fdd0766fd8725f4252186f5d0","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:48:28.000Z","msg":"加入風雲樂隊作新開始。據說黃耀光86年創作《吸煙的女人》參加亞太流行曲創作大賽時，原先打算找蔣志光做拍檔，但蔣志光和寶麗金簽了約，黃耀光才找陳德彰，而蔣以《我也不想說謊》同屆參賽但無獎，87年他在寶麗金推出EP後，轉投銀星唱片，與陳少偉、王利名組成第二代風雲樂隊。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5qn4Po1yEFo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5qn4Po1yEFo&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=9316fbbb\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/5qn4Po1yEFo</a><br />\n<br />\nEP的主打《拯救行動》是黃耀光作曲，另一首《你係我邊個》也是。蔣志光說過黃耀光是他的音樂啟蒙者。"},{"pid":"92684066d3f3674372d0e9a5f2303df4df8aa7df","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:48:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/aUz9wxzlsX0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FaUz9wxzlsX0&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=aed5a7a3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/aUz9wxzlsX0</a><br />\n<br />\n88年第二代風雲的《迷城》"},{"pid":"985b36b9c31a0fec53843dccff740fd1efee7c5f","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-lax3-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t31.0-8/fr/cp0/e15/q65/17546949_964542507013834_3255101370993050149_o.jpg?_nc_cat=111&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQmqAIn939kewKEyySb0ZRsJfkvxZvSJ9T59WhHWSUrI0tCftvyz41na8ENmpGLNSeEOaDed5wv-2c2TPiexavS3&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-lax3-2.xx&amp;oh=16a891f3142701f71f5424db8d395e7e&amp;oe=5E2F46C9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-lax3-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft31.0-8%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F17546949_964542507013834_3255101370993050149_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D111%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQmqAIn939kewKEyySb0ZRsJfkvxZvSJ9T59WhHWSUrI0tCftvyz41na8ENmpGLNSeEOaDed5wv-2c2TPiexavS3%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-lax3-2.xx%26oh%3D16a891f3142701f71f5424db8d395e7e%26oe%3D5E2F46C9&h=178016fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://2.bp.blogspot.com/-jjPAAN-dNT8/VOTN2xiTzRI/AAAAAAABDiA/I00rtEEVLcM/s640/IMG_4601.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F2.bp.blogspot.com%2F-jjPAAN-dNT8%2FVOTN2xiTzRI%2FAAAAAAABDiA%2FI00rtEEVLcM%2Fs640%2FIMG_4601.JPG&h=6ee39da6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n85年於林子祥首個演唱會扮林子祥，獲寶麗金賞識，展開創作歌手生涯，唱歌表演填詞作曲。甫出道，曾合組第2代「風雲樂隊」成為Raidas的隱形成員。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-22npWgXmig4/U-n_Y8vN6vI/AAAAAAAA0H8/vUynTxmI2GM/s640/cu0334.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2F4.bp.blogspot.com%2F-22npWgXmig4%2FU-n_Y8vN6vI%2FAAAAAAAA0H8%2FvUynTxmI2GM%2Fs640%2Fcu0334.jpg&h=28174b85&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"283b6448f00644ad79ae2de7f82a6b67e5041c22","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:49:34.000Z","msg":"萬片希望在明天 (1990) 飛圖 KTV<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yK39QmSGaJk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FyK39QmSGaJk&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=7aae78e4\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/yK39QmSGaJk</a><br />\n<br />\n『相逢』hit中，韋綺姍蔣志光再接再勵合唱，這次是發放正能量的《萬片希望在明天》，流行程度及不上第一次，但永高創意和飛圖極之喜歡推出合唱K歌，蔣志光韋綺姍成了固定拍檔。"},{"pid":"d5e314e5e54965f4b9c7f6ae55b05babed374a4b","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:49:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/fzta50c_G5Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Ffzta50c_G5Y&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=dac2a4d1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/fzta50c_G5Y</a><br />\n<br />\n《長路有多遠》<br />\n<br />\n滾石在台灣是一個好勁的音樂品牌，應該跟八九十年代的寶麗金差不多，90年代初起，滾石決定在港插旗 － 再不單止是將台灣的唱片拿過港發行，而是地道的製作廣東歌，在粵語唱片市場分一杯羹。<br />\n<br />\n但起初，滾石是先以子公司音樂工廠來港做先鋒，第一張雜錦星光煜煜、歌詞亦有新思維，是廣東唱片的經典。"},{"pid":"89f61afd858d1899f7ed79ab7d4c2e0497a65ec5","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:50:17.000Z","msg":"要走的始終都要走 (1990)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2A2x2ybtLL8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D2A2x2ybtLL8&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=b5e087c1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=2A2x2ybtLL8</a><br />\n<br />\n一星期叱咤冠軍，早過《相逢何必曾相識》上榜，不過後來被 『相逢』鋒頭蓋過。記得這首第一主打的人不多，歌曲結尾的英文和音是韋綺姍。她原本幫監製王利名唱廣告歌，聲靚獲賞識唱和音。『要走』的派台時DJ好奇打聽女和音是誰，監製立刻安排韋綺姍和蔣志光合唱『相逢』，造就這對經典合唱組合，和這首經典合唱歌。"},{"pid":"18c4525f2a4a59ec106ee7444fabf59b753ebb52","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:50:37.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/E2sgb15skj0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FE2sgb15skj0&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=6fda99cf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/E2sgb15skj0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/ANzHb68Fapo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FANzHb68Fapo&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqFI2fucNkJ94pdpDkYG0m8U%3D&h=d2676e4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/ANzHb68Fapo</a><br />\n<br />\n於89年為麥當勞拍的經典廣告，演釋「Rap住點餐」。20多年後，麥當勞再次邀請拍廣告，改編曲《相逢何必曾相識》。"},{"pid":"a6bac8ddf545f8c2e964e6dee4c5949f69e902af","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:51:23.000Z","msg":"【六四30】89年蔣志光親送《為自由》錄音帶上北京 見柴玲<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20190530/large/1559206441_4d0f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20190530%2Flarge%2F1559206441_4d0f.jpg&h=ad6d61c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n89年，冇WhatsApp、冇FaceTime，長途電話費貴到癲，而《為自由》一曲，盧冠廷5月22晚開工，一晚寫好，再由身在美國的太太唐書琛，透過長途電話填詞。5月23日早上，盧冠廷通知各唱片公司「吹雞」，梅艷芳逐個歌手打電話，羅文一收call即到。近百名歌手齊集EMI的錄音室錄了半天，約傍晚7時已錄好。"},{"pid":"283f6b0e0556f7d4622861ae3e4af138ee0152f8","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:51:40.000Z","msg":"錄好之後，兵分兩路，其一是製成錄音帶義賣，收益用於支持北京學生；其二是以不同方法，將之傳送到北京，方法包括：派人送到北京，或者用長途電話、播給留守天安門的學生聽，聽來頗不可思議，「人肉」方法誠然較可取，而這重任就交由前風雲樂隊成員蔣志光，及Raidas成員黃耀光負責，除錄音帶外還有一封支持學生的信，交給北京高校自治聯會。"},{"pid":"7f6265385290a211fac9fef519474d674cbf4b63","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:51:59.000Z","msg":"雖然北京氣氛緊張，但兩人稱過海關時比想像中容易。此行共逗留了4日3夜，還見到當時的天安門總指揮柴玲，多名學生虛弱得連打招呼都乏力。<br />\n<br />\n兩人甫返港即到跑馬地出席《民主歌聲獻中華》，上台分享，蔣志光說：「當我哋啱啱返落嚟嘅時候，聽到啲學生話聽日要撤退，其實我哋都覺得好唔開心，但最令我哋香港人驕傲嘅係，我哋真真正正可以拎到餅帶，全香港歌手唱嘅歌，係拎到上去！呢首歌，亦係天安門第一次播放嘅廣東歌！」振臂高呼。"},{"pid":"cf94d41f67428980d668770a6ddf210650758ad6","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T03:52:13.000Z","msg":"今次送帶上京，蔣志光感受極深。兩人抵達時已入黑，廣場上人影幢幢。學生們各樣資源已很緊絀，但仍留了飯盒給他們吃，但一入口有餿味，蔣志光即吐了出來，深感愧疚：「佢哋將珍貴嘅食物留畀你，但我食完仲要嘔&hellip;&hellip;」"},{"pid":"9613a6c67f379054467bf7a1de96ec1944d09f3e","tid":1591035,"uid":271234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T04:00:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">Brexit都係靠呢招食糊！</span><br />\n【眾籌 Youtube 廣告】 本地文宣 : 多媒體廣告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dRrFcS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dRrFcS</a>"},{"pid":"9399b7b83944b5708c82880dc9ebc189e5b2e971","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"覺得佢好似單立文，樂壇冇人氣走去拍膠劇 🙄"},{"pid":"043c0320eb63e8cbb5d8ed1146db9608c9620a38","tid":1591035,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T06:27:50.000Z","msg":"真係OUT曬,E家先第一次聽相逢何必曾Big Mac<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6cb768c270259c4884aff385b9751b4daa07974b","tid":1591035,"uid":211461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T07:24:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>EP的主打《拯救行動》是黃耀光作曲，另一首《你係我邊個》也是。蔣志光說過黃耀光是他的音樂啟蒙者。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拯救行動？<br />\n填滿海 填滿山 果隻？"},{"pid":"5ff8c8c9c1321e51c4de68b6dc015c76cf31c9ed","tid":1591035,"uid":301989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:08:59.000Z","msg":"佢是咪奶共"},{"pid":"2d2e3db98c67bba3e2228e5338755674d1321b67","tid":1591035,"uid":35221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:39:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dfcd21acbd94d548b0bd9c79ae115e709f47b46c","tid":1591035,"uid":265694,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9399b7b83944b5708c82880dc9ebc189e5b2e971","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T05:10:26.000Z","msg":"覺得佢好似單立文，樂壇冇人氣走去拍膠劇 🙄"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T08:52:30.000Z","msg":"冇計,佢真係完全唔靚仔,係九十年代既樂壇真係好難紅得起"},{"pid":"8a62b75ec45bff519fcf5ed768f9f78ad3553941","tid":1591035,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>EP的主打《拯救行動》是黃耀光作曲，另一首《你係我邊個》也是。蔣志光說過黃耀光是他的音樂啟蒙者。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n拯救行動？<br />\n填滿海 填滿山 果隻？</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/5qn4Po1yEFo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F5qn4Po1yEFo&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rA